channel.title: How do I figure out what port my server connects to?
channel.description: I have a no-ip, a source, and I can compile it and everything, I have opened up port 43594 on my router, so I'm wondering if my source uses a different port? Can anyone tell me how to find out and if it does, can I change it to 43594? Thanks in advance.
